window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Number one <i>New York Times</i> best seller.</p> <p>A modern, sophisticated suspense novel from National Book Award finalist, and Printz Award honoree E. Lockhart.&nbsp;Don't miss the eagerly anticipated prequel, <i>Family of Liars</i>, available May 2022!</p> <p>A beautiful and distinguished family.</p> <p>A private island.</p> <p>A brilliant, damaged girl; a passionate, political boy.</p> <p>A group of four friends - the Liars - whose friendship turns destructive.</p> <p>A revolution. An accident. A secret.</p> <p>Lies upon lies.</p> <p>True love.</p> <p>The truth.<br> <br> Listen to it. And if anyone asks you how it ends, just lie.</p>"; 
